\id 2PE
\h 2 Buṭrus 
\toc1 2 Buṭrus 
\toc2 2 Buṭrus 
\toc3 2 Bṭ. 
\mt1 2 Buṭrus  
\c 1
\s1 Řxedmet n Arebbi deg wuř n yinni dayes umnen  
\m
\v 1 Cimɛun Buṭrus, amsexxar d rrasul n Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, i inni ittwaḥesben am neccin ssdaheǧen l’iman s tsegda n Siditneɣ d Umsenjem nneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, ɛlaḥsab ccan d ijjen akidneɣ.   
\m
\v 2 Arḍa d řehna ad ɣarwem mmarenyen xmi i ɣa tessnem Siditneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Yḥ. 17:3; Rum. 1:7; 1 Bṭ. 1:2; Yah. 2. \x*  
\v 3 am Wenni iwcin marra min iǧan zi jjehd n AREBBI, maḥend ad yiwi Tudart d tiggʷudi zi AREBBI s tussna n Wenni d aneɣ dd-iřaɣan ɣar uɛuǧi nnes d lɛaḍama nnes,  
\v 4 d Wenni zzayes Netta iwca awem lwuɛud imɣaren iɣřan aṭṭas, ḥima ad zzaysen tcarcem di ṭṭbiɛet nnes n AREBBI, am tᵉttrakkʷarem zi nnecwat iɣeccen i yeǧan di ddunect. \x ◘ \xo 1:4 \xt Ica. 56:5; Yḥ. 1:12; Rum. 8:15; Gal. 3:26. \x*   
\m
\v 5 Am teǧa tmesřact ammu, arnim s marra cḍaret i l’iman nwem tcuni ifeyyḍen, i tcuni nwem ifeyyḍen tussna,  
\v 6 i tussna řewɛaret, i řewɛaret ṣṣbar, i ṣṣbar tiggʷudi zi AREBBI,  
\v 7 i tiggʷudi zi AREBBI tayri i wawmaten u i tayri i wawmaten tayri.  
\v 8 Mařa ttwafent daywem timesřayin-a uca ad daywem feyyḍent, war kenniw ttejjint texwam niɣ břa řɣiǧet di tussna n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:8 \xt Tit. 3:14. \x*   
\m
\v 9 Minzi wenni war ɣar ǧint tmesřayin-a, aqa iddarɣeř, minzi war ittwiři illa ittu asizdeg n ddnub nnes inni tuɣa xas. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Ica. 59:10; Ṣaf. 1:17. \x*  
\v 10 S uyenni, a aytma, cḍarem ktar ḥima ad tḍemnem tařaɣit d usixḍar nwem s řexdayem tiṣebḥanin, minzi mařa teggem aya, xenni ɛemmarṣ ad tenqarḍem.  
\v 11 Minzi ammu i d awem ɣa immarni s waṭṭas wadaf icnan ɣar tgeldit ittduman n Siditneɣ d Umsenjem nneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ.   
\b  
\m  
\s1 Amtan n l’iman nneɣ  
\m
\v 12 S uyenni war ttejjiɣ ad kenniw ssɛeqřeɣ zi man aya řebda, waxxa kenniw tessnem u aqa kenniw tbeddem \add x dsas n\add* tidett tanita.  
\v 13 Maca ittɣiř ayi nican min ɣa kkeɣ \add ɛad\add* di arrimet-a, ḥima ad kenniw ssfaqeɣ am ssɛeqřeɣ kenniw, \x ◘ \xo 1:13 \xt 2 Bṭ. 3:1. \x*  
\v 14 minzi ssneɣ aqa takessit n arrimet inu ad dd-tas deɣya, am mammec d ayi issargeb Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ. \x ◘ \xo 1:14 \xt Yḥ. 21:18, 19; 2 Tim. 4:6. \x*  
\v 15 Maca ad ggeɣ tizemmar, ḥima ad tɛeqřem x tmesřayin-a awarni uffuɣ inu.   
\m
\v 16 Minzi neccin war neḍfar ca tiḥuja isaysen, umi tuɣa d awem nettbarreḥ jjehd d twasit n Siditneɣ Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, maca aqa neched s tiṭṭawin nneɣ x lɛaḍama nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:16 \xt Mt. 17:1; Yḥ. 1:14; 1 Kur. 1:17; 2:1, 4; 4:20; 1 Yḥ. 1:1. \x*  
\v 17 Minzi Netta aqa iṭṭef zi AREBBI Babas ccan d uɛuǧi umi d as dd-tusa tmijja-ya zeg uɛuǧi i dd-yusin ak-d lɛaḍama nnes: “Wa d Mmi inu iɛizzen wenni dayes ufiɣ arḍa inu.” \x ◘ \xo 1:17 \xt Mt. 3:17; 17:5; Mk. 1:11; 9:7; Lk. 3:22; 9:35; Kul. 1:13. \x*  
\v 18 Uřa d neccin nesřa tmijja-ya zeg ujenna, umi tuɣa issawař akides, řami neǧa akides x wedrar iqeddsen.  
\v 19 Uřa d neccin ɣarneɣ awař d tidett n inabiyyen, \add u\add* kenniw ad teggem mliḥ mařa tewcim taynit i wawař nni am i yijj n řefnar yareqqen deg ijj n wemcan ibbubbes, ař ɣa idduqqez wass uca ad tenqar tfuct deg wuřawen nwem. \x ◘ \xo 1:19 \xt 2 Kur. 4:6; Asa. 22:16. \x*  
\v 20 Amezwar ittxeṣṣa kenniw ad tessnem aqa war din uřa d ict n nnubuwa tᵉnnufseř x tira nnes \add iqeddsen\add*.  
\v 21 Minzi min ittwanabben war dd-itteffiɣ ɛemmarṣ zi min ixs bnadem, maca yusa-dd \add zeg uqemmum n\add* yeryazen iqeddsen n AREBBI nni issiwřen am d asen dd-indeh Arruḥ Iqeddsen. \x ◘ \xo 1:21 \xt 2 Tim. 3:16. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 2
\s1 Ḥḍam ixef nwem zeg imseřmaden issxarriqen  
\m
\v 1 Maca tuɣa din ɛawed jar řgens inabiyyen issxarriqen, am mammec i ɣa iřin uřa d imesɣaren issxarriqen jar awem, ad ssidfen tibridin ittareddǧen, ad nkaren Sidi i ten isɣin, ad ssiwḍen \add ammu\add* areyyeb deɣya x yixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Aɛwd. 13:2; Mt. 24:11; Řex. 20:29; 1 Tim. 4:1; 2 Tim. 3:1. \x*  
\v 2 Aṭṭas i ɣa iḍfaren taxmuji nsen ař ɣa ittwaceqqef webrid n tidett zi ssibbet nsen.  
\v 3 S ṭṭmeɛ u s wawařen ittwaggen ad zzaywem ggen am zi sseřɛet, \add maca\add* řḥukm xasen zeg wecḥař uya war ibḍiř ca uca ahellek nsen war ittnudum ca. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Yah. 4. \x*   
\m
\v 4 Minzi mařa AREBBI war issar x \bd lmalakat\bd* i yeggin ddnub, maca inḍar i-ten di ssnaseř n taǧest di řaǧaɣ yuǧɣen uca isellem i-ten ḥima ad ttwaxemmřen ař řḥukm n uɛeddeb, \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt Yah. 6; Asa. 20:3. \x*  
\v 5 u \add ɛawed\add* war issar x \bd ddunect n zic\bd*, maca tuɣa iḥḍa Nuḥ, wenni d wiss tmenya, ambarreḥ n tsegda, řami dd-iḍřeq řḥemřet x ddunect n lkuffar, \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt Amz. 7:23; 1 Bṭ. 3:19. \x*  
\v 6 u \add ɛawed\add* řami issecmeḍ Netta \bd tineddam n Sadum d Ɛamurra\bd* u iḥkem xasent s uneqřeb, aqa yarra i-tent d lmital i lkuffar i ɣa yiřin ɛad. \x ◘ \xo 2:6 \xt Amz. 19:24; Aɛwd. 29:22; Ica. 13:19; Irm. 50:40; Ḥiz. 16:49; Ḥuc. 11:8; Ɛam. 4:11; Yah. 7. \x*   
\m
\v 7 Ɛawed issenjem Netta \bd Lut, amseggad\bd*, wenni tuɣa iweddben aṭṭas zi ticři ixemjen n yinni war ɣar teǧi ccariɛa. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt Amz. 19:7, 8. \x*  
\v 8 Maɣar umi amsegged wanita iẓra d isřa timegga nsen i war dd-yusin ak-d ccariɛa, ittwaɛeddab řeɛmar \add nnes\add* iseggden zeg wass ař wass, am tuɣa izeddeɣ jar asen. \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt Izhd. 119:158. \x*  
\v 9 \add Ammu\add* i issen SIDI mammec i ɣa issuffeɣ inni t itteggʷeden, zi řmeḥnet, \add maca\add* Netta iḥeṭṭa inni war iseggden ḥima ad ttwaɛeddben deg wass n lḥisab, \x ◘ \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Kur. 10:13. \x*  
\v 10 mahu qaɛ inni iḍfaren ddat \add nsen\add* am ttmeẓẓren di min ixemjen, u seḥqarran ṣṣulṭa \add n ijenwan\add*. Aqa aten d imɛeffaren d imneffxen, war ttarjijin zzat min iɛuǧen am ttceqqafen.  
\v 11 Waxxa lmalakat ujarent ten di ṣṣulṭa d jjehd, war xasen ssiwiḍent řḥukm n SIDI di ssibbet n uceqqaf.  
\v 12 \add Maca\add* nitni \add s řɛeks\add* ǧan am imuddaren ignawen ɛlaḥsab ṭṭbiɛet, inni yuran i tɣarṣt s řmus d tajeyyaft am ttceqqafen di min di war fehhmen. Ad ttwajeyyfen di tjeyyaft \add n yixef\add* nsen. \f ◼ \fr 2:12 \ft \+fk imuddaren\ft  - ixs ad yini ‘iwdan’ d ‘lḥayawanat’ d marra min iddaren nni izemmar ad yuyur.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt Irm. 12:3; Yah. 10. \x*  
\v 13 Ina d inni x teǧa řmuɛṣiyyet d řmunet i řmuɛṣiyyet. Nitni ḥesben tawarrit n meẓri deg nnecwat s uziř d abarreɛ am ccuren nitni s ibeqqiḍen \add n řewsex\add*. Xmi ttarran nnitni meẓri deg uraren nsen n uɣebbi, sellmen ixef nsen ɣar twarrit n meẓri tameqqrant.  
\v 14 Tiṭṭawin nsen ccurent s zzina u s ddenb war iqeṭṭin, xmi ɣekkwan nitni řeɛmur n yinni war ibedden nican. Aqa ɣarsen uř ittwarebban x ṭṭmeɛ, aqa nitni d tarwa n nneɛřet,  
\v 15 ffɣen zeg webrid iseggmen, weddaren, uca ḍfaren abrid nni ikka Balɛam, mmis n Faɣur, wenni tuɣa ittexsen řmunet n řɣecc. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt Řxř. 22:7, 21; Yah. 11. \x*  
\v 16 Maca netta iksi awebbex i řmuɛṣiyyet nnes, minzi zzayřet tagnawt tessiweř ɣares s ict n tmijja n iwdan, temneɛ tubbuheřya n unabi. \x ◘ \xo 2:16 \xt Řxř. 22:21. \x*   
\m
\v 17 Nitni d řɛunṣarat war dayes bu waman, d iseynuten ttwaɛarrnen s tḥaryaḍt, aqa tubbarcent n taǧest tᵉttwassewjed asen. \x ◘ \xo 2:17 \xt Yah. 12. \x*  
\v 18 Maɣar mařa ssiwřen s nnɛi n řhard \add nsen\add* ixwan, aqa nitni ssɣekkʷan s nnecwat ixemjen n arrimet inni igguren ad arewřen zeg inni isellmen ixef nsen i uɣekkwi.  
\v 19 Waɛden ten s tiřelli, waxxa nitni simant nsen d isemɣan n řɣecc. Minzi wi zi ittwaɣelleb bnadem, aqa i netta ad yiři d amsexxar. \x ◘ \xo 2:19 \xt Yḥ. 8:34; Rum. 6:16. \x*  
\v 20 Maɣar awarni řami dd-arewřen nitni zi řexmej n ddunect s tussna n Siditneɣ d Amsenjem nneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, aqa dewřen-dd ɣar řexmej nni ɛawed uca ttwaɣellben zzayes twařa nneɣni, aqa xenni aneggar nsen ad asen yura mahu x umezwar. \x ◘ \xo 2:20 \xt Mt. 12:45; Ɛbr. 6:4; 10:26. \x*  
\v 21 Aqa ḥsen asen meɛlik qqimen war ssinen abrid n tsegda zi min ssnen, uca řexdenni ad ffɣen ɛawed x tewṣeyyet iqeddsen i d asen dd-ittwasellmen.  
\v 22 Aqa temsar asen am tt iqqar wawař-a n tidett: “Aqzin aqa idweř-dd x min tuɣa dd-iɛuqq!” niɣ \add mammec d as qqaren nneɣni\add*: “Tiřeft tenni ittwassirden qaɛ, \add tedweř-dd\add* tᵉttmarraɣ deg ubaryuḍ \add nnes\add*!” \x ◘ \xo 2:22 \xt Awřn. 26:11. \x*   
\b  
\b  
\m  
\c 3
\s1 Ass n SIDI AREBBI  
\m
\v 1 \add A\add* imɛizzen inu, ta d tabrat wiss tnayen i d awem dd-uriɣ řexxu, u \add di tnayen n tebratin-a\add* arezzuɣ ad ssfaqeɣ nneyyet nwem iṣfan am kenniw ssɛeqřeɣ, \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt 2 Bṭ. 1:13. \x*  
\v 2 ḥima ad teqqimen tᵉttfekkarem deg wawařen nni tuɣa innan inabiyyen iqeddsen zic, uřa di tewṣeyyat n Siditneɣ d Amsenjem nneɣ, tinni \add ɣarneɣ dd-yiwḍen\add* s rrusul.  
\v 3 Man aya ittxeṣṣa ad tessnem d amezwaru, aqa deg wussan ineggura ad dd-asen imestehzayen inni istehzan am uyuren ɣar nnecwat nsen, \x ◘ \xo 3:3 \xt 1 Tim. 4:1; 2 Tim. 3:1; Yah. 18. \x*  
\v 4 ad inin: “Mani iǧa lwaɛd n twasit nnes? Zeg wami ṭṭṣen řejdud nneɣ, ammu i yeqqim kuřci am tuɣa iǧa zeg umezwar řami tᵉttwagg ddunect.” \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt Ḥiz. 12:22. \x*  
\v 5 Meɛlik ufin ad ttun belli s wawař n AREBBI aqa ijenwan izwaren ad iřin, u aqa řbarr igeɛɛed zeg waman u s ufus n waman s Wawař n AREBBI, \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt Amz. 1:9; Izhd. 24:2. \x*  
\v 6 \add aman\add* i zi tᵉttwahellek ddunect n řweqt nni umi dd xas ssefyen waman \add n řḥemřet deg wussan n Nuḥ,\add* uca tᵉttwamḥa. \x ◘ \xo 3:6 \xt Amz. 7:10, 21. \x*  
\v 7 Maca ijenwan d temmurt n yiḍa aqa ttwaḥefḍen s wawař nnes, xemmřen i tmessi ař ass n lḥisab d uweddar n lkuffar. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt Izhd. 102:27; Ica. 51:6; 2 Ts. 1:8; Ɛbr. 1:11; 2 Bṭ. 3:10. \x*   
\m
\v 8 Maca ittxeṣṣa kenniw war tᵉttᵉttum ict n řḥajjet, \add a\add* imɛizzen, aqa-tt d ta: ɣar SIDI ijj n wass am ařef n iseggʷusa uca ařef n iseggʷusa am yijj n wass. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt Izhd. 90:4. \x*  
\v 9 Aqa SIDI war issɛizzi deg usuffeɣ n řwuɛud nnes am mammec d asen ittɣiř i ca \add n iwdan\add*, maca Netta iggur akidwem s ttasiɛ n řxaḍar, minzi Netta war ittexs ca ad yareyyeb uřa d ijj, maca maḥend ad tuben marra. \x ◘ \xo 3:9 \xt Ḥiz. 18:32; 33:11; Ica. 30:18; Ḥab. 2:3; Rum. 2:4; 1 Tim. 2:4; 1 Bṭ. 3:20; 2 Bṭ. 3:15. \x*   
\m
\v 10 Maca ass n SIDI ad dd-yas am uxewwan s ǧiřet. Deg wass nni ad weddaren ijenwan s řɣefřet u timesřayin timezwura \add n ddunect\add* ad fesyent di tmessi uca tammurt d řexdayem i xas iǧan ad ttwafent. \x ◘ \xo 3:10 \xt Mt. 24:43,44; 1 Ts. 5:2; Asa. 3:3; 16:15. \x*   
\m
\v 11 Am marra timesřayin-a ad fesyent ammu, mammec ittcuwwar ad tuyurem kenniw s tqeddast d tiggʷudi zi AREBBI,  
\v 12 am tᵉttrajam tawasit n wass n AREBBI, am tᵉttmeẓrem dayes, xmi ɣa fnan ijenwan am ttwaqeǧben s tmessi uca ad fesyent timesřayin timezwura \add n ddunect\add* s řɛabuq nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Izhd. 50:3; 2 Ts. 1:8. \x*  
\v 13 Maca neccin aqa nettraja ijenwan n jdid d temmurt n jdid mani ɣa tezdeɣ tsegda ɛlaḥsab lwaɛd nnes. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Ica. 65:17; 66:22; Asa. 21:1. \x*   
\m
\v 14 S uyenni, \add a\add* imɛizzen inu, umi kenniw tᵉttrajam man aya, cḍarem maḥend ad tᵉttwafem břa řexmej u břa řɛib zzates di řehna.  
\v 15 Ḥesbem ttasiɛ n řxaḍar n SIDI d \add tawwart i\add* weṣřaḥ, am mammec uřa d umatneɣ iɛizzen Bulus d awem dd-yura ɛlaḥsab tiɣit i d as immewcen, \x ◘ \xo 3:15 \xt Rum. 2:4. \x*  
\v 16 am mammec xas issiweř netta di marra tibratin nnes. Aqa din ca n tmesřayin iwɛaren i řefhamet, tinni i ssfarraɣen řjuhhař d yewdan war imtinen \add deg wuř nsen\add*, am mammec ggin uřa i Tira \add Iqeddsen\add* nneɣni i wareyyeb n yixef nsen. \x ◘ \xo 3:16 \xt Rum. 8:19; 1 Kur. 15:24; 1 Ts. 4:15. \x*   
\m
\v 17 S uyenni kenniw \add a\add* imɛizzen inu, am tessnem man aya qbeř, ḥḍam ixef nwem, ḥima war tḍeffaram awarni i uweddar n yinni iǧan břa ccariɛa uca ad tewḍam waxxa tuɣa tᵉttbeddam nican,  
\v 18 maca \add s řɛeks ḥḍam\add* ad teymem deg arḍa d tussna n Siditneɣ d Amsenjem nneɣ, Yasuɛ Lmasiḥ, u n AREBBI, Babas, i Wenni umi ɣa yiři uɛuǧi, am řexxu am řebda, ař deg wussan n řebda! Amin.   